results.name: Write x/(1-x) in the form Sum_{j>=1} a(j)*x^j/(1+a(j)*x^j).
formula: a(n) = -Sum_t (-1)^v(t) where the sum is over all same-trees of weight n (see A281145 for definition) and v(t) is the number of nodes (branchings and leaves) in t.
results.author: _Gus Wiseman_, Aug 16 2017
